title: Cool Azir Montage I've made ;-)

embed.description: This is my 3rd Azir Montage, and also the first time me going hard on the editing ;-) I hope you'll like it. Most footage was taken from my smurf ^^ It took me 5 hours to render the clip and 1 hour to render the equalizer alone(And it's not a toaster.)

body: A montage I've spent quite some time on, I really like how it turned out :P
